name: PeripheralVascularDisease
title: Peripheral Vascular Disease
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains condition or diagnosis terms representing peripheral vascular disease conditions.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this set of values is to identify patients who have, or have had, a diagnosis of peripheral vascular disease.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes blood circulation disorders affecting the peripheral blood vessels only, outside of the the heart and brain.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes blood circulation disorders affecting central blood vessels (those affecting the heart and brain).)
